--- Lynxiz / Axis / Lokk ---

Lynxiz makes a grab at Trinity to take her to safety.

Axis pokes his head over the pod he is hiding behind, and picks a 
new target. He fires his laser twice at Stranato, and the follows up 
with a missile.

Lokk brings himself to a perch on the side of the mountain, behind 
the enemy. He bring out his machine guns, and picks a non 
engaged target. He sprays thirty bullets at Deemos.
